# Localhost and loopback URLs
http://localhost
http://localhost:*
https://localhost
https://localhost:*
http://127.0.0.1
http://127.0.0.1:*
https://127.0.0.1
https://127.0.0.1:*
http://0.0.0.0
http://0.0.0.0:*

# Example and placeholder URLs
http://example.com
https://example.com
http://example.org
https://example.org

# URLs that commonly return false positives due to bot protection
https://www.linkedin.com/.*
https://twitter.com/.*
https://x.com/.*
https://t.co/.*

# Sites that block automated requests or require authentication
https://discord.com/.*
https://discord.gg/.*
https://medium.com/.*

# npm package pages (often rate-limited)
https://www.npmjs.com/package/.*
https://npmjs.com/package/.*

# MCP endpoint URLs (not meant to be visited in a browser)
https://mcp\..*
